Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.10,0:00:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She thought that she could win, \Nbut there was no way. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.60,0:00:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Next year, \NI’ll be the fastest kid in the entire school!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.35,0:00:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s ‘cause I’m not in your school.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.65,0:00:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please! \NRemember last time \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.65,0:00:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,when I beat you in front \Nof the whole congregation?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.15,0:00:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Caleb, do you remember this story?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.56,0:00:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.60,0:00:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,that’s the Tower of Babel.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.27,0:00:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s right! \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.23,0:00:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why were these people \Ntrying to build this tower?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.35,0:00:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So they could live there?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.27,0:00:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.27,0:00:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,it was because they thought \Nthey were awesome \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.81,0:00:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and wanted to show off. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.40,0:00:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But what did Jehovah think of that?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he didn’t like it.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.85,0:00:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s right. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He even confused their languages \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.81,0:00:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,so they would stop bragging.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.48,0:00:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But at school everyone brags!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.15,0:00:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.77,0:01:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of people brag. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.15,0:01:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I have bragged too. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.19,0:01:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But that’s wrong. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.56,0:01:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,When we brag or show off, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.60,0:01:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,it’s like we are building \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.90,0:01:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,a tower for ourselves, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.40,0:01:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,just like the Tower of Babel.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.52,0:01:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If I wanted to, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.85,0:01:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I could set a new world record\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.40,0:01:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,—no problem!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.02,0:01:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say so. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.65,0:01:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But I’m better at basketball than you.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.52,0:01:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just messing around, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.56,0:01:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,but they say I’m a natural.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.10,0:01:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The higher up we try to put ourselves, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.40,0:01:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the more dangerous it gets. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.52,0:01:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know why?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.65,0:01:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we’ll eventually fall? \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.15,0:01:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, whoa. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.15,0:01:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.77,0:01:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooph!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.85,0:01:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.40,0:01:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, 1 Peter 5:5 \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.35,0:01:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,means that Jehovah \Ndoesn’t want us acting like \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.35,0:01:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,we are better than everyone else. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.48,0:01:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Humble people don’t need to brag, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.27,0:01:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,because Jehovah will make them \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.44,0:02:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,feel good about themselves \N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.98,0:02:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,on the inside.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.06,0:00:08.73,Default2,,0,0,0,,ほんとは あのこより\Nぼくのほうが はやい\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.73,0:00:11.98,Default2,,0,0,0,,らいねんは ぼくが\Nがっこうで 1ばんになる\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.98,0:00:14.94,Default2,,0,0,0,,ぼくが きみの がっこうに\Nいないからね\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.94,0:00:16.23,Default2,,0,0,0,,なに いってんの！\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.23,0:00:21.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,こないだ かいしゅう みんなの\Nまえで ぼくが かっただろ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.56,0:00:29.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,カレブ この おはなし\Nおぼえてる？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.44,0:00:32.40,Default2,,0,0,0,,うん\Nバベルのとう\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.40,0:00:33.56,Default2,,0,0,0,,そのとおり！\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.56,0:00:36.81,Default2,,0,0,0,,どうして このひとたちは\Nとうを たてようとしたの？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.81,0:00:39.77,Default2,,0,0,0,,それは……\Nすむため？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.77,0:00:42.27,Default2,,0,0,0,,ほんとは じぶんたちが\Nすごいってことを\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.27,0:00:45.19,Default2,,0,0,0,,みせびらかしたかったんだ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.19,0:00:48.06,Default2,,0,0,0,,でも エホバは\Nそれを どうおもった？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.06,0:00:50.15,Default2,,0,0,0,,うーん\Nいやだった\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:51.27,Default2,,0,0,0,,そう\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.27,0:00:55.10,Default2,,0,0,0,,それで ことばを こんらんさせて\Nじまんできなくしたんだ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.10,0:00:58.23,Default2,,0,0,0,,でも がっこうじゃ\Nみんな じまんしてるよ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.23,0:01:01.77,Default2,,0,0,0,,そうだね\Nじまんするひとが おおいね\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.77,0:01:04.60,Default2,,0,0,0,,パパも じまんしたことがある\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.60,0:01:06.40,Default2,,0,0,0,,でも それは まちがってる\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.40,0:01:08.94,Default2,,0,0,0,,じまんすることや みせびらかすことは\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.94,0:01:12.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,じぶんのために バベルのとうを\Nたてるようなものなんだ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.15,0:01:18.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,ぼくが ほんきになれば\Nせかいきろくだって らくしょうだ！\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.98,0:01:24.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,バスケットボールだったら\Nぼくのほうが ぜったい うまい\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.19,0:01:29.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,ぼくが ギターの てんさいだって\Nみんなが いってる\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.52,0:01:34.90,Default2,,0,0,0,,うえに いけば いくほど\Nどんどん あぶなくなるんだよ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.90,0:01:36.73,Default2,,0,0,0,,なぜだか わかる？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.73,0:01:38.94,Default2,,0,0,0,,いつかは おちちゃうから？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.94,0:01:41.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,わっ わっ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.90,0:01:44.52,Default2,,0,0,0,,わぁー\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.52,0:01:45.65,Default2,,0,0,0,,ふっ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.65,0:01:46.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,そう\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.56,0:01:50.02,Default2,,0,0,0,,それに ペテロだいいち\N5しょう 5せつで\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.02,0:01:51.65,Default2,,0,0,0,,みんなが えらそうにしないようにと\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:54.90,Default2,,0,0,0,,エホバは\Nねがっておられることが わかる\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.90,0:01:58.94,Default2,,0,0,0,,エホバは けんそんな ひとを\Nしあわせな きもちに してくださるから\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.94,0:01:58.94,Default2,,0,0,0,,だれも じまんしなくて いいんだよ\N
